∀ {V : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup V] [inst_1 : InnerProductSpace ℝ V] {p1 p2 p3 : V},
  p1 ≠ 0 →
    p2 ≠ 0 →
      p3 ≠ 0 →
        InnerProductGeometry.angle p1 p2 + InnerProductGeometry.angle p2 p3 + InnerProductGeometry.angle p3 p1 = Real.pi

  [inst_5 : Fact (FiniteDimensional.finrank ℝ V = 2)] {p1 p2 p3 : P},
  EuclideanGeometry.angle p1 p2 p3 + EuclideanGeometry.angle p2 p3 p1 + EuclideanGeometry.angle p3 p1 p2 = Real.pi

        EuclideanGeometry.angle p1 p2 p3 + EuclideanGeometry.angle p2 p3 p1 + EuclideanGeometry.angle p3 p1 p2 = Real.pi
